TY  - JOUR
T1  - Fluid, Fractured, and Distinctive? In Search of a Definition of Organizational Identity
AU  - Scott, Susanne G.
AU  - Lane, Vicki R.
Y1  - 2000/01/01
PY  - 2000
DA  - 2000/01/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.2000.27711619
